          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Access to Professional Education and Lifelong Learning Act or Access to PELL Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a program under which the Department of Education must award job training Pell Grants to students in job training programs and increases student assistance for working students.</p>]]></text>
